Judges - Young&rsquo;s Literal Translation (YLT) [1:1] And it cometh to pass, after the death of Joshua, that the sons of Israel ask at Jehovah, saying, `Who doth go up for us unto the Canaanite, at the commencement, to fight against it?&rsquo;
[1:2] And Jehovah saith, `Judah doth go up; lo, I have given the land into his hand.&rsquo;
[1:3] And Judah saith to Simeon his brother, `Go up with me into my lot, and we fight against the Canaanite &ndash; and I have gone, even I, with thee into thy lot;&rsquo; and Simeon goeth with him.
